2}, {\"ngram\": \"a mental breakdown\", \"from\": 951, \"to\": 969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Indeed,concentrating on the mental gymnastics of the sporthas been an important part of her routine.\", \"from\": 973, \"to\": 1073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the mental gymnastics\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporthas\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1034}, {\"ngram\": \"an important part\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1057}, {\"ngram\": \"her routine\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I journal, I go to therapy,\\\" the athlete added, \\\"and that's been the biggest game changer because there was a lot of self-doubt in there and a lot of pressure and a lot of not knowing where it all stemmed from.\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1286, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"therapy\", \"from\": 1095, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"the athlete\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1116}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest game changer\", \"from\": 1141, \"to\": 1165}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1184, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"self-doubt\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1203}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1222}, {\"ngram\": \"pressure\", \"from\": 1226, \"to\": 1234}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, to be able to talk about it, speak about it and know that it's OK to not be OK, it's a great feeling.\\\"\", \"from\": 1287, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a great feeling\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1391}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though every day is not easy, Suni is tumbling forward toward her goals.\", \"from\": 1395, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1425, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suni\", \"score\": 0.9999999998090061, \"rank\": 1.6722317796597072e-10, \"text\": \"Suni\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suni\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"