39, \"to\": 2446}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know how three years later it still has not.\\\"\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Heading to Paris, Suni does not need another medal to see how much she's accomplished (though she would not say no to a repeat victory.)\", \"from\": 2504, \"to\": 2640, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2515, \"end\": 2520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999999990905, \"rank\": 9.260068231866646e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2522, \"end\": 2526, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suni\", \"score\": 0.9999999998090061, \"rank\": 1.6722317796597072e-10, \"text\": \"Suni\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suni\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Suni\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another medal\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2554}, {\"ngram\": \"a repeat victory\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I would give myself a medal for not giving up,\\\" she noted.\", \"from\": 2642, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There has been so much that I could have given up on and so many things that have happened to where I could have just put this aside and moved on with my life.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many things\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2774}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2861}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But I wanted better for myself and I also wanted to be able to walk away from this Olympics or this quad knowing that I gave everything that I had and not regret anything.\\\"\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 3035, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Olympics\", \"from\": 2941, \"to\": 2954}, {\"ngram\": \"this quad\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2967}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 2988, \"to\": 2998}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3033}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This includes not giving up on her health journey, including as eczema.\", \"from\": 3037, \"to\": 3108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her health journey\", \"from\": 3068, \"to\": 3086}, {\"ngram\": \"eczema\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Which is why Sunipartnered with Eli Lilly and Company-the health equity sponsor of Team USA-to remind others with the skin condition that they are not alone.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3266, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3145, \"end\": 3150, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Wachowskis\", \"score\": 0.9999748093467714, \"rank\": 2.518932904861581e-05, \"text\": \"Lilly\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Wachowskis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Wachowskis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunipartnered\", \"from\": 3122, \"to\": 3135}, {\"ngram\": \"Company\", \"from\": 3155, \"to\": 3162}, {\"ngram\": \"the health equity sponsor\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"Team USA\", \"from\": 3192, \"to\": 3200}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 3211, \"to\": 3217}, {\"ngram\": \"the skin condition\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I was having a flare-up and it was very noticeable, I was always trying to cover it up with my makeup, which ultimately made it worse,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a flare-up\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3297}, {\"ngram\": \"my makeup\", \"from\": 3366, \"to\": 3375}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But being able to talk about it and also partnering with Lilly has been something so amazing for me mentally because I feel so much more confident in my own skin.\\\"\", \"from\"